                <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> Attio <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Tutori <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> alae I Bata<lb break="no" n="4"/><expan><abbr>vor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>miliar</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> alae I <expan><abbr>Tung</abbr><ex>rorum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Frontonian</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>uno</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>itum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> I B<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>etas</abbr><ex>iorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ivium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>omanorum</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urioni</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avia</ex></expan> Solva <lb n="10"/>Sedatius Quietus
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mittelteil einer Statuenbasis. Fundjahr: zwischen 1826 und 1831 in der zweiten Abbruchphase des Alten Turms. Ligaturen: Z. 6: Ligatur NI; Z. 10: Ligatur TI. Z. 8 (Ende): Buchstabe R klein in das C eingeschrieben.</p>
